## When to Use Tero.Ops

Tero.Ops is purpose-built for organizations where:

- Vessels or field sites operate with intermittent or zero internet connectivity
- Preventive maintenance must trigger on engine hours, fuel consumption, or calendar intervals
- ISM Code compliance records and certificate gap analysis are audit requirements
- Procurement spans multiple ports with partial deliveries across shipments
- A single platform must cover vessels, fish farms, and warehouse worksites under one company account

Tero.Ops is **not** a general-purpose project management tool. It is designed exclusively for physical asset operations in maritime and industrial environments.

